<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>318</hymn_number>
<title>HALLELUJAH! A DIH CH318</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A Fa Bawi Jesuh a zummi a dihlak kha, Pathian khamhnak lam a hun lai
 mi zapi ca'h.

[C1]
   Hal-le-lu-jah! Jesuh kha ka zumh ko. Pathian Fa Bawi Jesuh thi in a
   kan khamh cang! Hal-le-lu-jah! a dih, Jesuh kha ka zumh ko; Pathian Fa
   Bawi Jesuh thi in a kan Khamh cang.

[V2]
 Lam nih a har lai, tih awk um ko hmanhsehlaw, Ka Bawi Jesuh Khrih nih
 a ka zohkhenh sawk lai.

[C2]
   Hal-le-lu-jah! Jesuh kha ka zumh ko. Pathian Fa Bawi Jesuh thi in a
   kan khamh cang! Hal-le-lu-jah! a dih, Jesuh kha ka zumh ko; Pathian Fa
   Bawi Jesuh thi in a kan Khamh cang.

[V3]
 Ka dawtmi a tampi vancung ah an kal cang, Pathian inn chungah hi hla
 kha an nih an sa.

[C3]
   Hal-le-lu-jah! Jesuh kha ka zumh ko. Pathian Fa Bawi Jesuh thi in a
   kan khamh cang! Hal-le-lu-jah! a dih, Jesuh kha ka zumh ko; Pathian Fa
   Bawi Jesuh thi in a kan Khamh cang.

[V4]
 Ngakchia a tampi Pathian hmai-ka ah an dir, Teinak hla an sa i Bawipa
 kha an lawmh ko.

[C4]
   Hal-le-lu-jah! Jesuh kha ka zumh ko. Pathian Fa Bawi Jesuh thi in a
   kan khamh cang! Hal-le-lu-jah! a dih, Jesuh kha ka zumh ko; Pathian Fa
   Bawi Jesuh thi in a kan Khamh cang.

[V5]
 Sui phahmi lampi i hla an sak lioah khan, Khuazing kar-hlangtu le
 Siangpahrang kha ka hmuh.

[C5]
   Hal-le-lu-jah! Jesuh kha ka zumh ko. Pathian Fa Bawi Jesuh thi in a
   kan khamh cang! Hal-le-lu-jah! a dih, Jesuh kha ka zumh ko; Pathian Fa
   Bawi Jesuh thi in a kan Khamh cang.

[V6]
 Khi hla an saknak kaa chungah nangmah le keimah, Bawi Jesuh
 thangthatnak hla zungzal sa u si.

[C6]
   Hal-le-lu-jah! Jesuh kha ka zumh ko. Pathian Fa Bawi Jesuh thi in a
   kan khamh cang! Hal-le-lu-jah! a dih, Jesuh kha ka zumh ko; Pathian Fa
   Bawi Jesuh thi in a kan Khamh cang.</lyrics>
</song>